tualistes (en euros)"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"ORGANISMES"},{"type":"add","content":"(nom et numéro d'identification)"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"COTISATIONS"},{"type":"add","content":"brutes HT"},{"type":"add","content":"          du dernier exercice *"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"(hors opérations liées"},{"type":"add","content":"          à la durée de la vie humaine)"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"MOYENNE"},{"type":"add","content":"des prestations brutes"},{"type":"add","content":"          des trois derniers exercices *"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"(hors opérations vie)"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Organisme se substituant à d'autres mutuelles"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Organismes cédant leurs engagements par le biais de la substitution:"},{"type":"add","content":"- mutuelle ou union 1"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"- mutuelle ou union 2"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"- etc."},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Mutuelles et unions devant fusionner avec l'organisme repreneur:"},{"type":"add","content":"- mutuelle ou no 1"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"- mutuelle ou no 2"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"- etc."},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Total consolidé"},{"type":"add","content":"pour l'organisme repreneur (en euros)"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"* Pour les mutuelles antérieurement réassurées par l'organisme repreneur, indiquer les prestations et cotisations nettes (pour ne pas compter deux fois le même montant). Pour les mutuelles à garantir par le repreneur, n'indiquer que les prestations et cotisations relatives aux risques visés par la convention de substitution."},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Besoin de marge en fonction des cotisations brutes relatives aux opérations non vie et aux garanties complémentaires des opérations relevant des branches 20 à 22 :"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Le total des deux tranches de cotisations brutes (jusqu'à 10 M€ et au-delà de 10 M€) est multiplié par le rapport des dernières prestations nettes sur les dernières prestations brutes, ce multiple ne pouvant être inférieur à 0,50."},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Prestations du repreneur au dernier exercice (hors opérations vie)"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"montant brut"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"montant net"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"rapport net/brut"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"1o tranche"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"(18 % jusqu'à 10 M€)"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"2o tranche"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"(cotisations brutes - 10 M€) × 16 %"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Total des deux tranches multiplié par rapport net/brut"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Besoin de marge en fonction de la moyenne sur trois ans des prestations brutes relatives aux opérations non vie et aux garanties complémentaires des opérations relevant des branches 20 à 22 :"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Le total des deux tranches de prestations brutes (26 % de la moyenne des prestations jusqu'à 7 M€ et 23 % au-delà) est multiplié par le rapport des dernières prestations nettes sur les dernières prestations brutes, ce multiple ne pouvant être inférieur à 0,50."},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"1o tranche"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"(26 % de 7 M€)"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"2o tranche"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"(moyenne des prestations - 7 M€) × 23 %"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Total des deux tranches multiplié par rapport net/brut"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Pour la marge non vie, retenir le plus élevé des deux résultats ci-dessus."},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Besoin de marge pour les opérations vie (total des deux résultats ci-dessous)"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"1o résultat à partir des provisions mathématiques"},{"type":"add","content":"          et de gestion des opérations vie (cf. annexe I)"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"2o résultat à partir des capitaux sous risques"},{"type":"add","content":"          ou total des garanties décès souscrites (cf. annexe I)"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"montant brut"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"montant net"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"rapport net/brut"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"montant brut"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"montant net"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"rapport net/brut"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"1o résultat = (4 % du montant brut) × (rapport net/brut)*"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"2o résultat = (0,3 % du montant brut) × (rapport net/brut)**"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"* Si le rapport net/brut est inférieur à 0,85, retenir 0,85. De plus, lorsqu'il n'y a pas de risque de placement pour les fonds d'investissement, les fonds collectifs et l'épargne exprimée en unités de compte, multiplier les provisions par 1 % (et non 4 %)."},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"** Si le rapport net/brut est inférieur à 0,50, retenir 0,50. De plus, pour les garanties décès temporaires, multiplier les capitaux sous risque par 0,1 % (au lieu de 0,3 %) si la durée maximale est de 3 ans, et par 0,15 % si elle est de 4 ou 5 ans."},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Le besoin global de marge est égal au total des marges vie et non vie calculées ci-dessus."},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"NB : si les rapports \" net/brut \" doivent baisser pour l'exercice suivant la signature de la convention, remplir un 2o état."},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Références"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"  ### Articles faisant référence à l'article"},{"type":"add","content":"  "},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Arrêté du 6 février 2002 pris en application de l'article R. 211-23 du code de la mutualité - article 1 ENTIEREMENT_MODIF CREATION cible"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"  "},{"type":"add","content":"  ### Références faites par l'article"},{"type":"add","content":"  "},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"2002-02-06 CREATION source Arrêté du 6 février 2002 pris en application de l'article R. 211-23 du code de la mutualité - article 1 ENTIEREMENT_MODIF"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"Autres formats"},{"type":"add","content":""},{"type":"add","content":"* [JSON dans git](https://git.tricoteuses.fr/dila/donnees_juridiques/src/branch/main/LEGI/ARTI/00/00/21/00/07/LEGIARTI000021000709.json)"},{"type":"add","content":"* [Références JSON dans git](https://git.tricoteuses.fr/dila/references_donnees_juridiques/src/branch/main/LEGI/ARTI/00/00/21/00/07/LEGIARTI0000210